{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"2207f5431c8c6bd7291f9f","title":"P?? 语音生成中页面：陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367058,"created":1780371330025,"custom":{},"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-15_语音生成页陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"45c83867d23996e91387e9ab217ed351","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":3,"offset":579},"end":{"line":26,"column":40,"offset":616},"indent":[]},"value":"开发记录.2026-05-15_语音生成页陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录"}],"anchors":{"p-语音生成中页面陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"P?? 语音生成中页面：陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录","value":"p-语音生成中页面陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-背景":{"type":"header","text":"1. 背景","value":"1-背景","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"2-改动文件清单":{"type":"header","text":"2. 改动文件清单","value":"2-改动文件清单","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2},"3-技术方案演进":{"type":"header","text":"3. 技术方案演进","value":"3-技术方案演进","line":35,"column":0,"depth":2},"31-方案一lvgl-原生绘制小熊--恐龙":{"type":"header","text":"3.1 方案一：LVGL 原生绘制（小熊 → 恐龙）","value":"31-方案一lvgl-原生绘制小熊--恐龙","line":37,"column":0,"depth":3},"32-方案二bmp-rgb565-逐帧":{"type":"header","text":"3.2 方案二：BMP RGB565 逐帧","value":"32-方案二bmp-rgb565-逐帧","line":43,"column":0,"depth":3},"33-方案三最终方案lv_img_cf_indexed_4bit":{"type":"header","text":"3.3 方案三（最终方案）：LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_4BIT","value":"33-方案三最终方案lv_img_cf_indexed_4bit","line":53,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-详细改动":{"type":"header","text":"4. 详细改动","value":"4-详细改动","line":76,"column":0,"depth":2},"41-gen_dino_framespy--像素画生成脚本":{"type":"header","text":"4.1 gen_dino_frames.py — 像素画生成脚本","value":"41-gen_dino_framespy--像素画生成脚本","line":78,"column":0,"depth":3},"411-画布与调色板":{"type":"header","text":"4.1.1 画布与调色板","value":"411-画布与调色板","line":80,"column":0,"depth":4},"412-4-帧设计":{"type":"header","text":"4.1.2 4 帧设计","value":"412-4-帧设计","line":95,"column":0,"depth":4},"413-机器人结构布局":{"type":"header","text":"4.1.3 机器人结构布局","value":"413-机器人结构布局","line":104,"column":0,"depth":4},"414-输出格式":{"type":"header","text":"4.1.4 输出格式","value":"414-输出格式","line":123,"column":0,"depth":4},"42-dino_frames_bmph--帧表头文件":{"type":"header","text":"4.2 dino_frames_bmp.h — 帧表头文件","value":"42-dino_frames_bmph--帧表头文件","line":134,"column":0,"depth":3},"43-lv_example_meterc--ui-集成":{"type":"header","text":"4.3 lv_example_meter.c — UI 集成","value":"43-lv_example_meterc--ui-集成","line":154,"column":0,"depth":3},"431-新增头文件":{"type":"header","text":"4.3.1 新增头文件","value":"431-新增头文件","line":156,"column":0,"depth":4},"432-新增静态变量":{"type":"header","text":"4.3.2 新增静态变量","value":"432-新增静态变量","line":164,"column":0,"depth":4},"433-帧切换回调":{"type":"header","text":"4.3.3 帧切换回调","value":"433-帧切换回调","line":173,"column":0,"depth":4},"434-替换绘制函数":{"type":"header","text":"4.3.4 替换绘制函数","value":"434-替换绘制函数","line":186,"column":0,"depth":4},"435-清理逻辑增强":{"type":"header","text":"4.3.5 清理逻辑增强","value":"435-清理逻辑增强","line":224,"column":0,"depth":4},"5-未改动项":{"type":"header","text":"5. 未改动项","value":"5-未改动项","line":253,"column":0,"depth":2},"6-效果":{"type":"header","text":"6. 效果","value":"6-效果","line":263,"column":0,"depth":2},"7-flash-占用对比":{"type":"header","text":"7. Flash 占用对比","value":"7-flash-占用对比","line":291,"column":0,"depth":2},"8-注意事项":{"type":"header","text":"8. 注意事项","value":"8-注意事项","line":304,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"mfc3cj2sri7qmdu2uucoh2h","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"p-语音生成中页面陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录\">P?? 语音生成中页面：陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#p-语音生成中页面陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"p-语音生成中页面陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录-1\">P?? 语音生成中页面：陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#p-语音生成中页面陪伴机器人帧动画开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>日期</strong>：2026-05-15<br>\n<strong>工程</strong>：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code><br>\n<strong>编译命令</strong>：<code>scons --beken=bk7252n -j4</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-背景\">1. 背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>语音生成中页面（<code>VOICE_UI_GENERATING</code> 状态）此前使用 LVGL 原生绘制的卡通小熊 + 上下弹跳动画作为等待指示。效果粗糙、生硬，且 LVGL 原生几何体绘制能力有限，无法呈现丰富的角色细节。</p>\n<p>为提升产品\"陪伴感\"，需要一个更可爱的动画角色在 AI 生成语音内容期间展示，目标受众为 <strong>6-10 岁儿童</strong>。经过方案对比（小狗/小猫/恐龙/福星），最终选定 <strong>小机器人</strong>，因其方形几何结构在像素画中表现力最佳，且契合 AI 打印机产品调性。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-改动文件清单\">2. 改动文件清单<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-改动文件清单\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>文件</th><th>改动类型</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>applications/images/gen_dino_frames.py</code></td><td><strong>新增</strong></td><td>Python 像素画生成脚本，绘制 4 帧机器人并输出 C 数组</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/images/dino_frames_bmp.h</code></td><td><strong>新增</strong></td><td>帧图描述符头文件，暴露 <code>LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_4BIT</code> 格式图片及帧表</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/images/dino_frames_bmp.c</code></td><td><strong>新增</strong></td><td>4 帧 56×68 INDEXED_4BIT 像素数据，自动生成不手动维护</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/pages/lv_example_meter.c</code></td><td>修改</td><td>新增帧动画变量/回调/清理逻辑；替换小熊为机器人帧动画</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-技术方案演进\">3. 技术方案演进<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-技术方案演进\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-方案一lvgl-原生绘制小熊--恐龙\">3.1 方案一：LVGL 原生绘制（小熊 → 恐龙）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#31-方案一lvgl-原生绘制小熊--恐龙\"></a></h3>\n<p>最初尝试用 <code>lv_obj_create</code> + <code>lv_palette_main</code> 等 LVGL 原生 API 绘制卡通角色。先后尝试了小熊和恐龙，效果均不佳——几何体拼接感强，圆形/圆角矩形组合无法呈现\"可爱\"质感。</p>\n<p><strong>结论</strong>：放弃原生绘制路线，改用像素图片。</p>\n<h3 id=\"32-方案二bmp-rgb565-逐帧\">3.2 方案二：BMP RGB565 逐帧<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#32-方案二bmp-rgb565-逐帧\"></a></h3>\n<p>用 Python 脚本生成 4 帧 80×80 的 BMP RGB565 图片，编译进固件后用 <code>lv_img_set_src</code> 轮换。  </p>\n<p><strong>问题</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Flash 占用大</strong>：80×80×2 字节/像素 ≈ 12.8 KB/帧，4 帧 ≈ 51 KB</li>\n<li><strong>透明处理依赖 chroma-key</strong>：需将背景设为 <code>LV_COLOR_CHROMA_KEY</code> 纯绿（<code>0x00FF00</code>），LVGL 渲染时跳过该颜色。实际出现过品红背景（因脚本颜色常量写错）、白色卡片上透明色差等问题</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>结论</strong>：可用但 Flash 不友好，chroma-key 调试麻烦。</p>\n<h3 id=\"33-方案三最终方案lv_img_cf_indexed_4bit\">3.3 方案三（最终方案）：LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_4BIT<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#33-方案三最终方案lv_img_cf_indexed_4bit\"></a></h3>\n<p>LVGL v8 内置 <strong>4-bit 索引色格式</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>每像素仅 <strong>4 bit</strong>（2 像素打包为 1 字节）</li>\n<li>前 64 字节为 16 色调色板（RGBA8888 格式），之后为打包像素 nibble</li>\n<li><strong>天然支持 alpha 透明</strong>：调色板中背景色 alpha=0x00，其余颜色 alpha=0xFF</li>\n<li>无需 BMP 解码器，LVGL 直接渲染</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>数据布局</strong>：</p>\n<pre><code>[调色板 16×4=64B] [像素数据 (56×68+1)/2=1904B] = 1968B/帧\n</code></pre>\n<p>4 帧总计 <strong>~7.9 KB</strong>，比 BMP 方案省 <strong>~84% Flash</strong>。</p>\n<p><strong>尺寸优化</strong>：80×80 → 56×68，裁剪掉上下无用透明区域，进一步节省。</p>\n<p><strong>背景色</strong>：白色（<code>0xFFFFFF</code>），与语音面板 150×150 白色圆形卡片同色融合。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-详细改动\">4. 详细改动<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-详细改动\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"41-gen_dino_framespy--像素画生成脚本\">4.1 <code>gen_dino_frames.py</code> — 像素画生成脚本<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#41-gen_dino_framespy--像素画生成脚本\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"411-画布与调色板\">4.1.1 画布与调色板<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#411-画布与调色板\"></a></h4>\n<pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">W<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> H <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">56</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">68</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 最终尺寸</span>\n\nC_TRANS  <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rgb565<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0xFF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xFF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xFF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 背景白 → alpha=0</span>\nC_BODY   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rgb565<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0x90</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xCA</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xF9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 浅蓝身体</span>\nC_BODY_D <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rgb565<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0x5C</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x9C</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xE6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 深蓝（腿/天线杆）</span>\nC_FACE   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rgb565<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0xE0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xE0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xE0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 灰白脸盘</span>\nC_ANTENNA<span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rgb565<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0xF4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x43</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x36</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 红色天线球</span>\nC_EYE_BG <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rgb565<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0xFE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xFF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xFF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 近白眼白（与背景白区分，确保 alpha=0xFF）</span>\n</code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>背景纯白 <code>0xFFFFFF</code> 与卡片底色一致；眼白用 <code>0xFEFFFF</code> 微妙区分，确保索引色调色板中眼白 alpha 不被误设为 0。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"412-4-帧设计\">4.1.2 4 帧设计<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#412-4-帧设计\"></a></h4>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>帧</th><th>名称</th><th>动作</th><th>视觉特征</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>0</td><td>idle</td><td>待机</td><td>圆眼+高光、胸口绿灯、天线旁小星 ?</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>blink</td><td>眨眼</td><td>双眼变横线、身体微沉 1px</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>wave</td><td>挥手</td><td>右臂举过头顶、胸口灯变亮绿、动作弧线+大星</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>love</td><td>爱心</td><td>爱心眼(?)、天线变黄星、胸口脉冲、两颗漂浮 ?</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h4 id=\"413-机器人结构布局\">4.1.3 机器人结构布局<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#413-机器人结构布局\"></a></h4>\n<pre><code>        ?        ← 天线红球 (y=9)\n        |         ← 天线杆\n    ┌───────┐     ← 蓝头 + 灰白脸盘 (y=15~35)\n    │ ?   ? │     ← 眼睛 (y=23)\n    │  ___  │     ← 嘴巴 (y=28)\n    └──┬─┬──┘\n      ╱   ╲       ← 手臂\n    ┌───────┐     ← 身体 (y=41~59)\n    │ [?]  │     ← 胸口灯 (y=49)\n    └──┬─┬──┘\n     ┌┘ └┐       ← 腿 + 脚 (y=54~73)\n     └───┘\n</code></pre>\n<p>相对 80×80 版本，整体上移 14px，高度缩至 68px（头顶 y=4~9，脚底 y≈71~73），天线红球完整可见。</p>\n<h4 id=\"414-输出格式\">4.1.4 输出格式<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#414-输出格式\"></a></h4>\n<pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">write_indexed_c_array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buf<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> w<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># 1. 提取调色板（去重，限制 16 色）</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># 2. 背景白排第 0 位，alpha=0x00</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># 3. 其余颜色 alpha=0xFF</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># 4. 像素打包：高 nibble 为左像素，低 nibble 为右像素</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># 5. 输出 lv_img_dsc_t，.header.cf = LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_4BIT</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"42-dino_frames_bmph--帧表头文件\">4.2 <code>dino_frames_bmp.h</code> — 帧表头文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#42-dino_frames_bmph--帧表头文件\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">DINO_FRAME_COUNT</span> <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">4</span></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">extern</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_img_dsc_t</span> DINO_IDLE_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">extern</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_img_dsc_t</span> DINO_BLINK_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">extern</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_img_dsc_t</span> DINO_WIGGLE_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">extern</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_img_dsc_t</span> DINO_HAPPY_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_img_dsc_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> s_dino_frame_table<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>DINO_FRAME_COUNT<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>DINO_IDLE_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>DINO_BLINK_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>DINO_WIGGLE_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&#x26;</span>DINO_HAPPY_BMP<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>帧表 <code>s_dino_frame_table</code> 为 <code>static const</code>，在包含此头文件的每个 <code>.c</code> 中独立实例化，避免全局符号冲突，同时允许编译器内联优化。</p>\n<h3 id=\"43-lv_example_meterc--ui-集成\">4.3 <code>lv_example_meter.c</code> — UI 集成<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#43-lv_example_meterc--ui-集成\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"431-新增头文件\">4.3.1 新增头文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#431-新增头文件\"></a></h4>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"images/dino_frames_bmp.h\"</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>置于 <code>images/thermal_happy_lv.h</code> 之后。</p>\n<h4 id=\"432-新增静态变量\">4.3.2 新增静态变量<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#432-新增静态变量\"></a></h4>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* Dino frame animation */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_timer_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>s_dino_frame_timer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_obj_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>s_dino_frame_img<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span> s_dino_frame_idx<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"433-帧切换回调\">4.3.3 帧切换回调<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#433-帧切换回调\"></a></h4>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">dino_frame_timer_cb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">lv_timer_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_obj_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">lv_obj_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>t<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>user_data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    s_dino_frame_idx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">uint8_t</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_dino_frame_idx <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> DINO_FRAME_COUNT<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_img_set_src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_dino_frame_table<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>s_dino_frame_idx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>周期 200ms，4 帧循环一次约 800ms。</p>\n<h4 id=\"434-替换绘制函数\">4.3.4 替换绘制函数<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#434-替换绘制函数\"></a></h4>\n<p><code>voice_panel_generating_cartoon_pet()</code> 由原来的 LVGL 原生小熊绘制替换为：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">voice_panel_generating_cartoon_pet</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">lv_obj_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>slot<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_obj_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_obj_t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    pet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>slot<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_remove_style_all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">56</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">68</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_set_style_bg_opa</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_OPA_TRANSP<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_clear_flag</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_OBJ_FLAG_SCROLLABLE<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_add_flag</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> LV_OBJ_FLAG_OVERFLOW_VISIBLE<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">lv_img_create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_img_set_src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_dino_frame_table<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">lv_obj_center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    s_dino_frame_img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> img<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    s_dino_frame_idx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/* Frame cycle: ~200ms per frame */</span>\n    s_dino_frame_timer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">lv_timer_create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dino_frame_timer_cb<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/* Keep the gentle bounce on the pet root */</span>\n    s_vpanel_voice_anim_obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">voice_panel_start_generating_bounce</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>容器尺寸</strong>：56×68（与图片尺寸一致）</li>\n<li><strong>弹跳动画</strong>：继承原有 <code>voice_panel_start_generating_bounce</code>，translate_y 在 0 ? -6 之间缓动，周期 ~1s</li>\n<li><strong>两层动画叠加</strong>：容器弹跳 + 内部帧切换，形成\"蹦蹦跳跳的机器人\"效果</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"435-清理逻辑增强\">4.3.5 清理逻辑增强<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#435-清理逻辑增强\"></a></h4>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">voice_anim_cleanup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_vpanel_voice_anim_obj <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">lv_anim_del</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_vpanel_voice_anim_obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        s_vpanel_voice_anim_obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_dino_frame_timer <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">lv_timer_del</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s_dino_frame_timer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        s_dino_frame_timer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    s_dino_frame_img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    s_dino_frame_idx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>在原有 bounce 动画清理基础上增加帧 timer 销毁和图片指针置空。<code>voice_anim_cleanup</code> 在以下场景被调用：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>语音面板重建（<code>voice_panel_rebuild</code>）</li>\n<li>语音状态切换（<code>voice_ui_apply_under_lock</code>）</li>\n<li>界面销毁（<code>ui_destroy_layers</code>）</li>\n<li>二级桌面刷新（<code>second_desktop_refresh_center</code>）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>确保离开生成状态后 timer 立即停止，无内存泄漏和野指针。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-未改动项\">5. 未改动项<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-未改动项\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>voice_panel_icon_slot_layout</code></strong>：图标槽尺寸和布局逻辑不变</li>\n<li><strong><code>voice_panel_footer_labels</code></strong>：底部文字（\"AI 生成中...\" + 副标题）不变</li>\n<li><strong><code>voice_panel_build_generating</code></strong>：调用 <code>voice_panel_generating_cartoon_pet</code> 的入口不变</li>\n<li><strong><code>voice_ui_state_t</code> 枚举</strong>：<code>VOICE_UI_GENERATING</code> 状态定义不变</li>\n<li><strong>LVGL 配置</strong>：<code>lv_conf.h</code> 中 <code>LV_IMG_CF_INDEXED_4BIT</code> 为 LVGL v8 内置支持，无需额外启用宏</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-效果\">6. 效果<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-效果\"></a></h2>\n<p>语音生成中页面，150×150 白色圆形卡片内：</p>\n<pre><code>┌─────────────────────────────┐\n│       ? (天线红球+星)       │\n│     ┌───────┐               │\n│     │ ?   ? │  ← 圆眼/眯眼/?│\n│     │  ___  │               │\n│     └──┬─┬──┘               │\n│      ╱│ │╲   ← 挥手帧右臂举起│\n│    ┌───────┐                │\n│    │ [?]  │  ← 胸口灯闪烁   │\n│    └──┬─┬──┘                │\n│      │ │    ← 整体上下弹跳   │\n│     ┌┘ └┐                   │\n│     └───┘                   │\n├─────────────────────────────┤\n│      AI 生成中...           │  ← 文字\n│      请稍候片刻             │\n└─────────────────────────────┘\n</code></pre>\n<p>4 帧以 200ms/帧循环（800ms 一周期），容器以 520ms 周期上下弹跳（translate_y 0?-6px），两个动画相位错开，形成自然灵动的陪伴效果。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"7-flash-占用对比\">7. Flash 占用对比<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#7-flash-占用对比\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>方案</th><th>格式</th><th>单帧</th><th>4帧</th><th>透明方式</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>方案二</td><td>BMP RGB565 (80×80)</td><td>~13 KB</td><td>~51 KB</td><td>chroma-key</td></tr><tr><td><strong>方案三（最终）</strong></td><td><strong>INDEXED_4BIT (56×68)</strong></td><td><strong>~2.0 KB</strong></td><td><strong>~7.9 KB</strong></td><td><strong>alpha 通道</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>固件总大小 2312 KB（app 分区），帧动画数据占比约 0.34%，几乎可忽略。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注：<code>gen_dino_frames.py</code> 脚本不参与编译，仅开发阶段使用。运行时 <code>dino_frames_bmp.c</code> 为编译产物。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"8-注意事项\">8. 注意事项<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#8-注意事项\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>修改帧图</strong>：编辑 <code>gen_dino_frames.py</code> 中的 <code>draw_robot</code> 函数，运行 <code>python3 gen_dino_frames.py</code> 重新生成 <code>.c/.h</code>，再编译即可。无需手动编辑 C 数组。</li>\n<li><strong>调整帧速</strong>：修改 <code>lv_timer_create(dino_frame_timer_cb, 200, img)</code> 中的 <code>200</code>（毫秒）。值越小越快。</li>\n<li><strong>颜色限制</strong>：INDEXED_4BIT 最多 16 色（含透明）。当前 12 色，有 4 色余量可添加新颜色。</li>\n<li><strong>设计师替换</strong>：如需设计师提供像素画，可提供 56×68 的 PNG 模板，由脚本导入替代 <code>draw_robot</code> 生成逻辑；或设计师直接出 INDEXED_4BIT 格式的调色板+像素数据替换 <code>dino_frames_bmp.c</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/\">root</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI 打印机固件文档库","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"e5d7823b7368b844c5d7bde821080751","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":83},"end":{"line":8,"column":20,"offset":100},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.项目交接资料","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":115},"end":{"line":9,"column":18,"offset":130},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.项目交接资料"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"阶段性开发总结","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":145},"end":{"line":10,"column":14,"offset":156},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"阶段性开发总结"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"tutorial","position":{"start"